Package: opencpu
Title: Embedded Scientific Computing and Reproducible Research with R
Version: 1.6.7.9000
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen@berkeley.edu>
License: Apache License 2.0
URL: https://www.opencpu.org
    https://github.com/jeroen/opencpu#readme
